{"tid":1708193,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"罷課問卷，對抗囚徒困境","createTime":"2019-11-11T13:35:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-12T08:52:55.000Z","uid":242734,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"6392a7884fce9ca66d8be6d23cbb7295e84c4442","tid":1708193,"uid":242734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T13:35:02.000Z","msg":"今日香港重演64事件，交警對手無寸鐵巿民開三發實彈，另一地方交警用電單車衝撞人群，前線為大家幫手罷工，願意用性命設路障，為既就係怕被炒魷魚既打工仔，怕會失attendance 既大學生，怕被老師罰既中學生。<br />\n<br />\n前線受傷，如果你無罷課其實你都有份害佢地食彈。<br />\n<br />\n如果你願意罷課，朋友見你罷課跟住你罷，其他人見多人罷就跟著罷，造成蝴蝶效應，打工仔見大學生願意罷課，鼓起勇氣罷工，打擊經濟支柱，前線就不用冒生命威脅設路障。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n下面就係一份表格填寫你願唔願意罷課<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLScRdYIh0Os6BYkxxZOn6Qv8aItXkMoxFv91aqpDAcPTH7f6FQ/viewform?usp=sf_link\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fforms%2Fd%2Fe%2F1FAIpQLScRdYIh0Os6BYkxxZOn6Qv8aItXkMoxFv91aqpDAcPTH7f6FQ%2Fviewform%3Fusp%3Dsf_link&d=KwnMNtvToZrWMgCiTfGJQRckzRVyZutP2gug%2B5Lqx%2Fc%3D&h=6422393a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLScRdYIh0Os6BYkxxZOn6Qv8aItXkMoxFv91aqpDAcPTH7f6FQ/viewform?usp=sf_link</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n兩日後會公佈結果"},{"pid":"fe61c7797353b4fc39621bf03cf5e7fc006dd459","tid":1708193,"uid":242734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T13:38:50.000Z","msg":"如果結果證明大家都係怕無人罷所以唔罷<br />\n<br />\n咁我份問卷就可以話比大家知其實好多人罷！！！！！！！"},{"pid":"39fd63e6afd6049516c3cfa2086090842bdb0a12","tid":1708193,"uid":242734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T13:40:09.000Z","msg":"幫手推下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7911f3b73017141112cccec952d0640496b0d23b","tid":1708193,"uid":85396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T13:46:17.000Z","msg":"建議問卷簡單解釋下咩係囚徒困境<br />\n手足send出去都方便啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad5850fd36a5b5f3ac49948e6bfa4aaf4ee854a9","tid":1708193,"uid":31